📱 SL TABLET HUD (MOAP SYSTEM)
🧠 Developer Task Sheet + Build Plan
1. 🎯 PROJECT OVERVIEW
Goal:

Build a HUD-based tablet interface inside Second Life using MOAP that functions like a simplified smart device with:

Messaging (SL IM + optional external chat system)
YouTube viewer
Weather app
Marketplace viewer
Web browser (restricted/safe)
Optional Discord bridge (external integration)
2. 🧱 SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE
📦 FRONTEND (Second Life HUD)
Single or multi-prim HUD (tablet shape)
One main MOAP screen (display surface)
Button-based navigation (link clicks or touch regions)
App router script (switches pages)
LSL Responsibilities:
Handle UI interactions
Switch MOAP URLs
Send HTTP requests
Trigger SL IM notifications
🌐 BACKEND (External Server)

Used only for advanced features:

Discord OAuth / API bridge (optional)
Weather API handler
Messaging database (chat system)
Marketplace data proxy
Web page rendering for MOAP apps
